show.title: Meri Mohabbat, Mera Inteqam
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/CfSa5T
show.description: When Arjun Malhotra crosses paths with a mystic fakir, he’s thrust into visions of a past life of love, betrayal, and a death that never let go. As his present unravels and memories of Nisha resurface, buried truths collide with unfinished karma. In a world where second chances are rare, “Meri Mohabbat, Mera Inteqam” is a gripping tale of rebirth, redemption, and the cost of finally remembering who you were. Watch Now!
